title: Capcom Fighting Evolution.iso (NTSC) (PS2)
description:
Capcom Fighting Evolution
Playstation 2
Capcom

1-2 Players
Memory Card - 43 KB
Digital/Analog Control
Vibration Function

Legendary fighters from five Capcom arcade classics finally meet in one totally old-school game! This all-new game lets you choose from characters spanning Street Fighter II, Street Fighter III, Street Fighter Alpha, Darkstalkers, and Red Earth/Warzard.
